{"tid":2174682,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"柳俊江證林卓廷到場前白衣人已施襲 ：如林卓廷參與暴動為何主動報警？","createTime":"2020-08-26T04:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T12:46:37.000Z","uid":240362,"like":565,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":120,"replies":[{"pid":"835af05738ab37886949993137f97a85423d70f9","tid":2174682,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:44:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/M6Z6REUU7FBFVKBMDFNUFOJVCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FM6Z6REUU7FBFVKBMDFNUFOJVCQ%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDuSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=9e9cc9fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FM6Z6REUU7FBFVKBMDFNUFOJVCQ%2F&h=6d8c336b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/M6Z6REUU7FBFVKBMDFNUFOJVCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n林卓廷由「原告變被告」，被警方指去年7.21涉「暴動罪」被捕，警方的濫捕無底線，引來各界嘩然。撰寫《元朗黑夜》、在7.21也同告受傷的柳俊江亦在Facebook撰文，指「暴動罪」能泛指參與「破壞社會安寧」的非法集結，指林卓廷作為立法會議員，到場履行監察責任，如何「破壞社會安寧」？而若林卓廷真的要破壞社會安寧，為何到場前後都主動報警？他繼而指，如指控林參與暴動，是否代表所有在場市民都參與暴動，而非發動「恐怖襲擊」的白衣人一方？最後，柳反問拘捕林的行動是真正有足夠檢控證據基礎，還是支持警隊輿情的政治操作？"},{"pid":"c96f51f07147601a10a457915841fb64b4c2f21a","tid":2174682,"uid":43751,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:46:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c905590a102a798445e021b53d15b91a8b5b0e99","tid":2174682,"uid":21545,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"晏啲拉埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f275b37eb86182a524af77407c78a491d316f4e7","tid":2174682,"uid":91897,"like":130,"dislike":2,"score":128,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"黑警：柳俊江你成頭血又係現場，下個到你"},{"pid":"c739254aff027d9d33ad096373e48bf39e36b00f","tid":2174682,"uid":4312,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"警：OK，拉漏左柳俊江，遲d 補番"},{"pid":"6cc72ca1e2b60c2daadf2